{"tid":1474337,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何方妖葉劉淑儀支持透過法律手段以緊急條例禁止示威","createTime":"2019-08-15T06:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:48:07.000Z","uid":26275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e4d68b0ab7a526f1fd5d0e962a392e6065dafb","tid":1474337,"uid":26275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:45:30.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員兼新民黨立法會議員葉劉淑儀表示，警隊面對現時的局面很艱難，相對消防和救護，警隊的工作較有爭議，她又指，有人怪責警隊處理示威太軟弱和出動太慢，也明白有市民對警方的處理有不滿，但認為警方可以調動的人不多，要靠警隊承擔保護安全的責任。<br />\n<br />\n她在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，聯合國人權專員早前對香港警方使用催淚彈的講法，只是回應示威人士的投訴，又指對方未有實地了解，很難透過片段作評論。她又認為，現時年輕人可能誤解何謂自由，自由是要有秩序和尊重他人，希望他們可以和平散去，不用政府出動更嚴厲法例處理示威。<br />\n<br />\n對於星期日當晚接受傳媒訪問時指，警方不可能喬裝示威者，葉劉淑儀解釋，當日是對喬裝的講法感到錯愕，又指，網上好多消息和流言，事後理解認為警方以「放蛇」的方式處理，也不是不合理，強調警方不會做違法的事。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方未有跟隨港澳辦的講法，表示香港有恐怖主義的苗頭，葉劉淑儀認為，示威者掟氣油彈行為很危險，又批評襲擊警察宿舍的行為很恐佈。被問到行為恐佈是否等同恐怖主義，葉劉淑儀說，她並沒有作界定，承認現時的情況未達法例對恐怖主義的定義。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀表示，現時香港的事態非常嚴重，又支持另一名行政會議成員湯家驊提出，透過法律手段，以緊急條例禁止示威，止暴制亂，重申過往香港被評為最安全的城市，現時招牌被「打爛」，令人非常痛心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474790-20190815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474790-20190815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdndT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=22af2680\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474790-20190815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9723525e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474790-20190815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap241&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdndT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=9567d35d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國之將亡必有妖葉劉淑儀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a002e6804c4d3c45b577a1bd2732c0240faa3f5","tid":1474337,"uid":304321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:47:14.000Z","msg":"姐姐依家老是常出現"},{"pid":"9a85453344e64759705b37574947e70c518fd089","tid":1474337,"uid":26275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a002e6804c4d3c45b577a1bd2732c0240faa3f5","tid":1474337,"uid":304321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:47:14.000Z","msg":"姐姐依家老是常出現"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"成日想拎存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}